Changed ActivityEdityLocationMap and FragmentEditLocationMap to communicate through an interface

Some code cleanup
Some code cleanup
Some code cleanup

Adding test reviews and associated instrumentation tests
Adding test reviews and associated instrumentation tests
Updated TestReviewsTest to work
Fixed test reviews not tagging reviews correctly
In the process of getting aggregation to view properly
In the process of getting aggregation to view properly
Fixed a bug that stopped aggregated data expanding to reviews list
Got rid of tree flattener as no longer needed
Some code cleanup
Fixed tests that relied on TreeFlattener which has been removed
Cleaned up gradle file a bit
Fixed a bug that would cause app to crash if returning from build screen via up then reentering build screen via plus. Due to review builder not being discarded properly.
some code cleanup
Added a one button dialog in prep for having share functionality on the feed screen. made GvData view dialog a one button dialog
Added dialog to feed screen that pops up on long click. Oprions are share, edit, delete. Only delete works at the moment.
Changed text views in share edit dialog to be buttons
Some code cleanup
Some code cleanup

Can publish to social platforms via long click dialog on feed screen. Added twitter formatter

PublishButtonAction wasn't added for commit
Fixed bug in buildscreenmodifier. was using wrong share ui
ome code cleanup
In the process of trying to use Twitter API programatically from hShare screen
